s=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]\u003Cbr id=\"al2-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">⁦ - - - - - - - - - - ⁩\u003C/span>]\u003Cbr id=\"al3-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">3\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">⁦ - - - - - - - - - - ⁩\u003C/span>]\u003Cbr id=\"al4-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">4\u003C/span>.ΑΣ\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Θράσυς Ἐμ\n                    μενίδας Δορι\n                    στόνφο̄ν\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"idionym\" data-text=\"Θράσυς\">ΘΡΑΣΥΣ\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Ἐμ\n                    μενίδας Δορι\n                    στόνφο̄ν\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"patronym\" data-text=\"Ἐμ\n                    μενίδας\">ΕΜ\u003Cbr id=\"al5-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">5\u003C/span>ΜΕΝΙΔΑΣ\u003C/span>ΔΟΡΙ\u003Cbr id=\"al6-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">6\u003C/span>ΣΤΟΝΦΟ̄Ν\u003C/span>\u003C/span>ͰΑΠ\u003Cbr id=\"al7-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">7\u003C/span>ΑΝΤΟ̄ΝΕΣΤΙͰΥ\u003Cbr id=\"al8-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">8\u003C/span>ΠΕΡΤΑΤΟΣΑΚΙΔ\u003Cbr id=\"al9-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">9\u003C/span>ΟΝ\u003C/span>\u003C/div>\u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"facsimile-images\">\u003Ch2>Facsimile Images\u003C/h2>\u003Ca href=\"ISic030142_tiled.tif\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic030142_tiled-thumb.tif\">\u003C/a>\u003Ca href=\"ISic030142.jpg\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic030142-thumb.jpg\">\u003C/a>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"apparatus\">\u003Ch4>Apparatus criticus\u003C/h4>\u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan>  \u003Cspan>Text after Cassio 1994 with minor emendation of Cordano 2020\u003C/span>  \u003C/span>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"translation\">\u003Ch2>English translation\u003C/h2>\u003Cp class=\"translation-author\">  \u003C/p>\u003Cp>  \u003C/p>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"translation\">\u003Ch2>Italian translation\u003C/h2>\u003Cp class=\"translation-author\">  \u003C/p>\u003Cp>[...] Thrasys Emmenidas di tutti i coraggiosi con la lancia è il migliore degli arcieri (trans. Cordano)\u003C/p>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"commentary\">\u003Ch2>commentary\u003C/h2>  \u003Cp>This document is physically and archaeologically distinct from the tesserae with which it was originally published, from a different context in the sanctuary of Athena at the archaeological site of Kamarina. The revised reading of Cassio, followed by Cordano makes it a dedication by Thrasys for his success with the bow.\u003C/p>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"bibliography\">\u003Ch2>bibliography\u003C/h2>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli> 42.0846 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Cordano 1992 6 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002437\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002437\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Cassio 1994 5-20 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002762\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002762\u003C/a>  \u003C/li>\u003Cli> Cordano 2020 263-266 fig.2 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002276\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002276\u003C/a>  \u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli> 52.0920 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epi